  "original_title": "\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0bc7\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bcd,  \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba9\u0bcd  \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "D Rajendar, Uruthirakumaran meet!",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Prime Minister of the Transnational Government of Tamil Eelam V. Uruthirakumaran met Mr. T. Rajendar, a multi-talented film director and supporter of Tamil Eelam, who was visiting America for medical treatment. He was admitted to the hospital for the past few days and is now recovering and resting.",
        "In addition to expressing his friendship and support for the struggle for justice and political sovereignty of the Elamites, he has led many protests in Tamil Nadu. Prime Minister V. Uruthirakumaran, who is resting after completing advanced treatment, thanked him for his support to the struggle of Elamites. He wished him a long life and return home.",
        "Mr. Lokes, Mr. Karuna, Mr. Kamal, Mr. Kalaiyarasi, members of the Subcommittee of the Transnational Tamil Eelam Government in New York, and Mr. Bala Swaminathan, President of the Council of North American Tamil Associations also participated in this meeting.",
        "D. Rajender, who emotionally expressed his feelings on the Eelam independence struggle, said that he was happy to meet Eelam relations in New York. Mr. Bala Swaminathan, who has taken over as the new president of the North American Council of Tamil Associations, also conveyed his congratulations."
      ],
